data.description: $15,000 REDUCTION FROM ORIGINAL LIST PRICE!!!  Discover tranquility in your new haven at Holly Pointe! Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this residence strikes the perfect balance between serenity and accessibility. Close to essential amenities such as grocery stores, entertainment venues, dining options, shopping destinations, and easy access to I-75, this home offers convenience without sacrificing privacy. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, with an additional bonus room upstairs perfect for a home office, craft haven, or casual retreat, this dwelling accommodates your every need. Step through the inviting front door into a spacious foyer, connecting seamlessly to the kitchen and living area. The living space, adorned with vaulted ceilings, lends an airy atmosphere and overlooks the formal dining area. The charming kitchen, complete with a welcoming island and breakfast bar, beckons you to gather for warm conversations. Tucked away at the rear of the home, the Owner's Suite offers a private sanctuary with an accompanying bathroom for unwinding after a long day. Two additional bedrooms, strategically separated from the Owner's Suite, share a generous hall bathroom, ensuring added privacy. Outside, the expansive backyard beckons with a patio and an outbuilding featuring a lean-to, creating an intimate gathering spot around the outdoor chimney. Zoned for Houston County High School, this home exudes charm and warmth. Seize the opportunity – call today to schedule your exclusive tour of this captivating residence!
